The Summer of Love

-The so called ‘Summer of Love’ took place in the summer of 1967 in the Haight-Ashbury neighborhood of San Francisco -Thousands of young people migrated to the neighborhood -By the end of the summer problems of disease and youth homelessness ran rampant -On the upside, a lot of great music was made
